Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:35.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitsugaya's advance troops\Nhave remained in Karakura Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:37.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and a new Arrancar\Nhas appeared before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:42.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This Arrancar is a troublesome enemy\Nbecause he clones himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:47.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitsugaya and the others manage\Nto drive off the first group of Arrancars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:52.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that appear and protect, Shota and Yui,\Na pair of souls who are siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,According to an analysis\Ndone in Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:04.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,this Arrancar controls\Nseveral clones at once
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:07.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to absorb\Nas many souls as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:09.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:10.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:15.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:28.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'm not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:36.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here!\NWe've got to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:46.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:47.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:49.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll look for Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:52.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect Yui myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:18.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui! What were you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to come to this park.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're here,\NI'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I...ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui... I left her here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day of the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:04.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We got separated\Nfrom mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui and I were so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day,\Nwe looked everywhere for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:22.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But we couldn't find them\Nno matter where we looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yui!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yui!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui went to go\Nlook for them by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:50.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yui!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yui!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:02.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yui!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother! Help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait! Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother, help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:47.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trembling somewhere\Nfar away from the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:57.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui was...\NBecause I ran away, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I...really regretted what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered up the courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I went to the park...\Nbut Yui wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it showed up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's Yui?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who knows?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give Yui back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:40.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look for her yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You punk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:59.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! Let me go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:07.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I...abandoned Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:13.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that,\NYui still says that I'll protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Rangiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was tough, wasn't it, Shota?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not certain what to make\Nof what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but at least Yui was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And she got to see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:41.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:47.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if Shota's story is true...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason why Yui\Nencountered the Mock Arrancar{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was probably because...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:03.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I went after the Mock Arrancars,\Nbut they got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking care of a soul\Nwho was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:13.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him whether he knew anything,\Nbut he's so terrified he can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll head back too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We'll meet up at...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:25.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm taking care of a soul\Nwho was attacked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:47.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be that it transformed\Ninto a human soul?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's how it stayed hidden\Nand attacked souls...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't follow his Spiritual Pressure either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a call from Rangiku...\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have become troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:24.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the details\Nafter we go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I just let my guard down\Nand dropped my Soul Pager.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Madarame?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's keeping watch over the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:46.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...There's something\Nthat I've been wondering about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you've\Nbeen wondering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:51.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... It might have something to do\Nwith the appearance of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right... I'll listen to\Nwhat you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The first...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Taking the date and the time\Ninto consideration...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:04.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a very high possibility\Nthat the first person
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that the Mock Arrancar\Nencountered was Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did she survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like\Nshe even remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya,\Nwhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I've figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:34.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have anything to do with\Nwhat we're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:35.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:41.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that these Mock Arrancars\Ncan transform into human souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:42.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By transforming into human souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:50.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they can hide their Spiritual Pressure\Nand escape the watch of Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:56.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably approached human souls\Nin their transformed state
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:59.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to catch them off their guard\Nand absorb their spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:03.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They use that power\Nto multiply even further.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:07.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, by cloning themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:11.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it is possible for these Mock Arrancars\Nto absorb many souls at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They can gather\Nan incredible amount of power
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:15.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They can transform into humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:20.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:23.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Shota...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still not sure\Nif that is the case, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:42.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:47.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't perform a Konso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:55.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:12:00.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...I...I...\Ndon't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:01.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Captain...\N- It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- The Arrancar has definitely\N- Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,done something to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:11.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, we don't know\Nwhen she'll show her true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:20.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have Soul Society examine this child's\NSpiritual Pressure immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We now have all\Nthe reishi samples we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:31.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:36.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected the Mock Arrancars\Nto become the people they attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:41.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're increasing\Ntheir power in that manner,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and waiting for\Nthe right time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:47.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find and crush the main body\Nbefore that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:48.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll contact you as soon as\NI get results from the analysis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we get those results...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:13:00.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have her stay\Nwithin a kido barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:06.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! You're locking her up?!\NYou can't! I feel sorry for Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:10.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota, this is for Yui's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:14.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Arrancar has\Ndone something to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they might even be after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a way we can protect her.\NDon't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:26.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's in the barrier,\Nthe enemy cannot get to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:32.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. We'll defeat the Arrancar\Nin the meantime. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui, bear with this\Nfor a little while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:42.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm...kind of scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:47.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a little different\Nfrom the one you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... This is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you wait inside the barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... If Yui's fine with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:08.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:15.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's settled,\NI'm going to trade off with Ikkaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:19.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll trade off with Madarame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasegawa,\Nyou go to Urahara's Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:23.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara's Shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Abarai the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:27.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, take care of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:32.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what\Nthe enemy is going to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is almost at its peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep well, Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, I want to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:57.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I want to let you out,\Nbut I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see them, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:13.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get out of here with your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:16.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:22.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, did you discover anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:47.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much. Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as we suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:01.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui, Shota... Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some traces\Nof Spiritual Pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the barrier broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose that the kids did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About your request...\NWe have the results.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:25.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, you go look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up with you\Nafter I hear what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are the results?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:37.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've concluded that\NYui Toyokawa is a clone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}created by the Mock Arrancar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:47.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably had strong potential\Nspiritual power as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:54.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It all began when she encountered\Nthe Mock Arrancar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:58.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that\Nthe Mock Arrancar absorbed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui Toyokawa's spiritual power\Nby chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:05.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Arrancar then had\Nan explosive gain in power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:08.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and developed the ability\Nto multiply its clones
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and gather power for its main body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:15.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He then used that method\Nto increase his power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:19.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in a short amount of time by\Nabsorbing a large amount of souls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:20.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:25.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seemed like that girl\Nwas moving of her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the enemy is controlling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:30.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- There's a high possibility that it's all an act.\N- Say, Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:31.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- If that's the case...\N- Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we destroy the main body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll disappear too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's what it means.\N- Just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:45.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yui Toyokawa has\Nstrong spiritual power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then what about\Nher older brother, Shota?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:53.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a possibility for relatives\Nto have the same level of spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She used Shota's power\Nto break my Kyomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is after\NShota's spiritual power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shota... Where did you go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:11.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota! Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you break that barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:22.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was easy to get out of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:28.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:32.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:06.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:08.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're all prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:30.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my body\Nmoving on its own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:55.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:09.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:13.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:24.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:29.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:31.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui?! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:22.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Akon, there's a letter from\NThird Seat Madarame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:25.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,asking when the item he ordered\Nis going to be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:25.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His order?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:26.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted molars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NWe'll send him this empty box
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:32.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and tell him that they're molars\Nthat are invisible to idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:33.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:37.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Arrancar Encyclopedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:42.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Today I'm going to tell you\Nthe Arrancar's numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:45.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,UNDECIMO               TRECE\N\N\NQUINCE              DIECISEIS\N\N\N	The Arrancars are numbered\N	according to their birth order,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:48.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,according to their birth order,\Nstarting from eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:49.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,DIEZ                                 \N\N\NThe ones with particularly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:53.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,SEIS                                  \N\N\Ndeadly killing abilities\N	are numbered from one through ten
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:56.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by order of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:58.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,ESPADA\N\N\NThose ten are called the Espada.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:01.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just between you and me,\NUlquiorra's number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not the time to reveal that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:04.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no fun.